item.title: People of ProsperUS: Shayla Davis
item.description: People of ProsperUS: Shayla Davis By:Â Anna Gotskind Unik I Am strives to empower and uplift young women to embrace their journey and not let mistakes define who they are. Founder, Shayla Davis, accomplishes this through motivational speaking about her own experiences and providing support services to help women find housing, jobs, and more. Unik I Am’s mission is to seek to uplift, empower, and motivate women to understand and embrace their struggles, success, failures, mistakes, and achieve their goals.
